// TESLA_FLEET_CLIENT_ID, TESLA_FLEET_CLIENT_SECRET) and a new top-level
// `signed_command_paths` block describing Fleet/Hermes availability plus
// per-vehicle path recommendations. Every v3 field path is preserved
// unchanged; downstream MCP consumers reading v3 shape still find their
// fields. See U5 of the 2026-05-22-001 plan.
